snippet.title: A Rite From The Stars - Gameplay Video [English]
snippet.description:
This is the First Gameplay Video of A Rite fromt he Stars, graphic adventure and first project of Risin' Goat. We show the basic mechanics that define the game. Stay tuned! News coming soon.
